# Floating Add [Single]

A-Form

* fadds FRT,FRA,FRB (Rc=0)
* fadds. FRT,FRA,FRB (Rc=0)

Pseudo-code:

    FRT <- FPADD32(FRA, FRB)

Special Registers Altered:

    FPRF FR FI
    FX OX UX XX
    VXSNAN VXISI
    CR1          (if Rc=1)

